s always efficient and essential, with few samples and no useless effects, often using the Roland TB 303 to produce mind-boggling, hypnotic odysseys. \n\n <a href=\"https://www.last.fm/music/Emmanuel+Top\">Read more on Last.fm</a>. User-contributed text is available under the Creative Commons By-SA License; additional terms may apply."}}}